Requirements Are...
-------------------

1) ANY Classic AMIGA with a minimum of 2MB of mixed memory, (a stock A1200).
2) Extra Floppy drive or optional HDD.
3) Standard OS2.0x to 3.9x.
4) Amiga Forever 5 or greater.
5) ~Project6~ from ~TestGear2.lha~ in the ~hard/hack~ drawer of AMINET.
6) ~WinUAE-ADC.lha~ in the ~hard/hack~ drawer of AMINET.
7) Numbers 5) and 6) are NOT required for the default ~DEMO~ mode.
8) Workbench MUST be in at least 16 Colours AND 640x200 resolution minimum.

