TestGear 7, Project 17, Data-Logger/Transient Recorder...
---------------------------------------------------------

Overview:-
----------

(Note ADC = Analogue to Digital Converter.)

This project is a Data-Logger/Transient Recorder that uses a Parallel Port
ADC or Games Port ADC. If neither are available then the software defaults
to a ~DEMO~ mode that simulates Parallel Port usage.

The Parallel Port ADC is ONLY for classic AMIGAs and is as fast as the
~DEMO~ mode. It samples at about 100 Samples/Second for a standard A1200,
much faster on faster AMIGAs.

The Games Port ADC works on classic AMIGAs AND WinUAE and was primarily
designed for WinUAE usage. The fastest sample rate for this version is
about 1 Sample/Second so the Transient Recorder mode is unavailable.

